td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Mænd: haft anal eller oral sex med en anden mand?</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Kvinder: haft seksuel kontakt med en mand, der har haft anal eller oral sex med en anden mand?</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Har du inden for de sidste 2 måneder:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\